dct_title_s: British dominions in America : drawn from the latest and best authorities
dct_description_sm: Scale not determined Relief shown pictorially. Shows areas occupied by many Native American tribes. Above neat line: Engrav'd for Guthrie's new geographical grammar. Date of publication from McCorkle. Map was also included in 1782 ed. Probably issued in: A new system of modern geography ... / by William Guthrie ... London : Printed for C. Dilly ...; and G.G. and J. Robinson ..., 1780.
dct_publisher_sm: [London : Printed for C. Dilly ... ; and G.G. and J. Robinson ... , 1780]
